OL,3,CHarvard morgue manager who sold body
OL,4,Cparts like 'baubles' jailed for 8 years
OL,6,FA former manager of the Harvard
OL,7,FMedical School morgue in Boston, USA,
OL,8,Fhas been sentenced to eight years in
OL,9,Fprison for stealing and selling body
OL,10,Fparts "as if they were baubles".
OL,12,FUS authorities said Cedric Lodge was
OL,13,Fat the centre of a disturbing scheme
OL,14,Fin which he shipped brains, skin,
OL,15,Fhands and faces to buyers in
OL,16,FPennsylvania and elsewhere after
OL,17,Fcadavers donated to Harvard were no
OL,18,Flonger needed for research.
