OL,6,FHis wife, Denise Lodge, was sentenced
OL,7,Fto just over a year in prison for
OL,8,Fassisting him. They appeared on
OL,9,FTuesday in court in Williamsport,
OL,10,FPennsylvania.
OL,12,FIn one example, Cedric Lodge provided
OL,13,Fskin to a buyer so it could be tanned
OL,14,Finto leather and bound into a book, a
OL,15,F"deeply horrifying reality," Assistant
OL,16,FUS Attorney Alisan Martin said in a
OL,17,Fcourt filing.
