OL,6,FLodge, who was a morgue manager for 28
OL,7,Fyears, expressed regret in court.
OL,8,FDefence attorney Patrick Casey said
OL,9,Fhis acts were "egregious."
OL,11,F"Mr Lodge acknowledges the seriousness
OL,12,Fof his conduct and the harm his
OL,13,Factions have inflicted on both the
OL,14,Fdeceased persons whose bodies he
OL,15,Fcallously degraded and their grieving
OL,16,Ffamilies," Casey said in a court
OL,17,Ffiling.
OL,19,FHarvard suspended the donation of
OL,20,Fbodies for five months in 2023 when
OL,21,Fcharges were filed.
